description: Malcolm and Ramsey have a little bit of a crush on each other, and it showed throughout the day, especially with Malcolm. His excitement to be inside Ramsey was pretty clear, “Yeah, I mean, wouldn’t you be?” He couldn’t keep his hands to himself, so we had to shorten our little walk in the great outdoors to get back to the house and get things started…
title: Malcolm & Ramsey: Bareback
